messages.subject: Quick update
messages.msgSnippet: Just wanted to pop in real quick and say hi to everyone...and sorry for being a lousy list owner and not keeping up with posts. We ve made the move to
messages.messageBody:
Just wanted to pop in real quick and say hi to everyone...and sorry
for being a lousy list owner and not keeping up with posts.

We've made the move to Tennessee and we're freezing our butts off!!:)
It's so beautiful here though, and we LOVE our new house. I especially
love that we live only 3 hours from Ben and Kelly now. Yippeeee!!

Through all the stress of moving there have been some really lovely
unschooling moments. I wish I had time to write them all down, but
Trevor is already antsy to have his computer back (hey, it didn't take
me that long to get rid of over 200 emails!!).

The kids are loving it here, now I need to hook up with some cool
unschoolers. Brandi?:)

Ren
